### Admin Get Users List
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/get-users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 10,
  "search": "",
  "is_active": true,
  "is_verified": true,
  "role": "admin"
}

Notes:
- Optional filters supported: search, skill_name_new, gender, department, role, is_active, is_verified.
- Boolean-like fields (is_active, is_verified) accept true/false or 1/0 (or string variants).

### Admin Get Customers List
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/get-customers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 10,
  "search": "",
  "is_active": true,
  "is_verified": true,
  "role": "customer"
}

Notes:
- Same optional filters as users: search, skill_name_new, gender, department, role, is_active, is_verified.

### Admin Update User Status
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/update-user-status/:id
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": true
}

### Admin Delete User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/user/:id
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Admin Get Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/notification?skip=0&limit=10&is_read=false
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

Notes:
- Added optional is_read query parameter to filter notifications by read state (true/false or 1/0).
- Pagination params: skip and limit.

### Admin Read Notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/notification
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notification_id": "notification_id_here"
}
